'''Prison Compound 32''' was a [[Prison/Legends|prison]] used by the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] to keep their prisoners of war. A group of prisoners, led by members of the [[Naboo Underground]], managed to [[Escape from Prison Compound 32|escape]] the compound.

